{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_08_01",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　嘘でしょ？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……いきなりどうしたんだ？）\n（あっちに誰かいるのか？）",
      "startTime": 5.8220801728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あの人は――",
      "startTime": 8.226856478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "初音ミク……！",
      "startTime": 9.9682850996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが、ライブツアーのために",
      "startTime": 12.8269928533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "北海道にやってきた時のこと",
      "startTime": 14.6669926132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0869919378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、さっきは驚いたよ",
      "startTime": 16.9936600922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "東京からはるばる北海道まで来たからには\nそりゃ、何か面白いことがないかなって期待してたけど",
      "startTime": 23.8904928006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.0405990044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、街でばったりミクに会うとは思わなかったよ\n期待してた以上の驚きだ",
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3554287354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、葵もミクを知ってたんだな\nミクの動画を観てた感じもなかったし、意外だったよ",
      "startTime": 38.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕の方こそ、君があんなに驚くとは思わなかったよ\nまぁ、事務所で聴いてたことはないから仕方ないけど",
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.500711894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "大体ゲーセンで音ゲーをやって覚えたからね\nミクの曲は大人気で、沢山収録されてるから",
      "startTime": 55.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほどな。そう言えば前に）\n（葵に音ゲーを勧めたことがあったっけ）",
      "startTime": 62.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1647933404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そのミクが僕達のライブに出てくれるって言うんだから\nどこでどう縁が繋がるか、分からないもんだ",
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "縁と言えば……昔、麻奈のマネージャーになる前に\n人気アイドルのライブを観に行ったんだ",
      "startTime": 79.1374662686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6408742666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "……へぇ",
      "startTime": 82.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その人気グループのメンバーとは今こうして話してて\nライブのために一緒に北海道まで来てる",
      "startTime": 87.0666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9057210047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、縁がどう繋がるかなんて\nその時になってみないと分からないもんだよなぁ",
      "startTime": 92.8333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、そうかもね",
      "startTime": 96.1210727453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.3503017266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "君と僕達の縁と同じくらい\nミクとの縁も、長くいいものになることを願うよ",
      "startTime": 102.0999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3103016693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、まずはライブ本番まで頑張らないとね\nミクに恥ずかしいところは見せられないから",
      "startTime": 110.3333323161,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4336.129108899996,
          "startTime": 114.669461425
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.6676838999965,
          "startTime": 115.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4361290454
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4361290454
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.669461425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、ミーティングの末、リズノワはミクと一緒に）\n（ライブで新曲を披露することになった）",
      "startTime": 119.4333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（今、リズノワとミクで一緒に新曲を作ってるはずだけど）\n（打ち合わせはうまく進んでいるだろうか……）",
      "startTime": 126.3333307902,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6692098000167,
          "startTime": 129.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、{user}君\n午後からライブのスタッフと会議って言ってなかった？",
      "startTime": 132.5132587592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、俺の方はどうにか終わったよ\nそっちは……新曲の進捗はどうだ？",
      "startTime": 138.9640708445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.4153189818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "作詞作曲はミクを中心に進めてるし……\nああ、さっきまでミクとダンス対決をしてたんだよ",
      "startTime": 145.9666732788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.8353507518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "た、対決！？",
      "startTime": 149.8353507518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "あ、別に喧嘩したとかそういう訳じゃないよ",
      "startTime": 151.6113483508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.472890385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "いいものを作るには意見をぶつけ合うことも必要だって\nミクも分かってくれたからね",
      "startTime": 159.4666936239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、建設的な対決で良かったよ\n……それで、どうだったんだ？",
      "startTime": 165.8000269573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.8550898313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "うん。ミクは凄いね\nあの子を見てたら、僕もますます燃えてきたよ",
      "startTime": 170.9333602906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "葵がそこまで言うなら、よっぽど凄いんだな",
      "startTime": 175.2033666371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.3413712262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "単純に技術が高いのはまぁ、当然として\nなんて言うのか、動きが軽やかなんだ",
      "startTime": 183.4000269573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、バーチャル・シンガーだもんな\n同じ振り付けでも違って見えるのか",
      "startTime": 190.9000391643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.7530836819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。他にも、どんなダンスも抜群にうまいし\nずっと動きにキレがある。表現力だって凄いんだ",
      "startTime": 198.2000391643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "後はキラキラ光ったと思ったら、一瞬で衣装が変わった\nりね。それを見てたら、僕も負けていられないなって",
      "startTime": 206.3873776757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.5590473572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "それは軽やかとはちょっと違うような……\n……というか、そこで張り合わなくても",
      "startTime": 214.6333724976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに衣装早着替えはやってないよ\n普通にダンスでセッションしただけさ",
      "startTime": 221.2667058309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 223.9794555425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "僕がこう……くるっと回ったら\nミクもこう、片足でターンしてきて",
      "startTime": 226.9333724976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "ミクの長い髪がふわっと宙を舞ったら\n僕はこう、大きく腕を広げて動いてみたり",
      "startTime": 233.3667058309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.8067119676
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ、楽しかったなぁ……\nまぁ、気がついたら莉央達はへばってて",
      "startTime": 241.5000391643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 245.1600452819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "こころなんか「葵さん、飛ばし過ぎです～」なんて\n泣き言まで言ってたよ",
      "startTime": 249.2667058309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "はは……無理し過ぎても良くないから、ほどほどにな\nそれで、新曲の振り付けの構想はまとまったのか？",
      "startTime": 256.2333724976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 260.1170528808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "うん。せっかくミクと共演するんだから――",
      "startTime": 260.1170528808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けだって、重力なんかに囚われない\n軽やかでダイナミックな動きにしたいよねって",
      "startTime": 267.0333724976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 270.333515636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi028.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、本番まであんまり時間はないけど……\nいつも通り、最高のステージに仕上げてみせるよ",
      "startTime": 274.1333724976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "それは頼もしいな\nライブ当日を、楽しみにしてるよ",
      "startTime": 279.9000391643,
